beer.beer_description: Page Turner is a brand new Oat Cream double IPA, which we have lovingly caressed with a sultry hop combination that includes Yakima Chiefs Cryo Pop Blend #1, Centennial, Cashmere and Motueka. This baby is thick, creamy and a full on juicy banger. Cryo Pop brings a huge intensity of overripe mango, creamy passionfruit with a juicy fruit bubblegum hit of cashmere. A smooth and silky mouthfeel keeps things slick and helps to saturate the palate with all the fruit intensity that comes with each sip. This is definitely a banger.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
